<p>
    I was born in Lucknow, which is a city in the northern part of India. Very early in childhood, my
    family relocated to a hill station called Nainital, which is in the mountainous region of the Himalayas. When I was in 5th grade
    I moved to a boarding school called Birla Vidya Mandir (BVM).
</p>

